sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant UI as Web/App UI
    participant API as Account Service
    participant DB as Account DB
    participant Bank as Core Banking System

    User->>UI: Request to create new bank account
    activate UI
    UI->>API: Submit account creation details
    activate API
    API->>DB: Validate user and check eligibility
    activate DB
    DB-->>API: Eligibility confirmed
    deactivate DB
    API->>Bank: Create bank account
    activate Bank
    Bank-->>API: Account created (accountId)
    deactivate Bank
    API->>DB: Persist account record
    activate DB
    DB-->>API: Account persisted
    deactivate DB
    API-->>UI: Return account confirmation
    deactivate API
    UI-->>User: Show new account details
    deactivate UI